import React from 'react' import Button from "@material-ui/core/Button" import DialogContent from '@material-ui/core/DialogContent'; import DialogContentText from '@material-ui/core/DialogContentText'; import DialogTitle from '@material-ui/core/DialogTitle'; import Paper from "@material-ui/core/Paper" import Grid from "@material-ui/core/Grid" const Beatmaps = ({beatmaps}) => { beatmaps.sort((a, b) => (a.difficulty > b.difficulty) ? 1 : -1) console.log(beatmaps) return (
{beatmaps.beatmaps[0].title} {beatmaps.beatmaps.map(beatmap => ( {beatmap.title}, by {beatmap.mapper}. AR {beatmap.difficulty_ar} ))}
) } export default Beatmaps
